agentData.mission: Develop a detailed experimental design and analysis plan to co-optimize vehicle architecture and energy-management control across representative ICE/HEV/PHEV/BEV architectures. Specify the architectures to compare, standardized drive cycles and user-behavior scenarios, objective functions and constraints, required simulation and hardware-in-the-loop (HIL) experiments, data collection metrics, and the methodology for producing Pareto fronts and sensitivity analyses.
